1. *Mojom* majkom je svejedno ko će biti naš novi domaćin. (My mother doesn't care who will be our new host.)

2. Radila je malo za *mojom* firmom. (She worked a little for my company.)

3. Kupila sam novu haljinu za *mojom* malom sestrom. (I bought a new dress for my little sister.)

4. On je bio savršen za *mojom* prilikom. (He was perfect for my occasion.)

5. Smestio se je u *mojom* stanu. (He settled in my apartment.)